msgid "Return to The Midnight Masks"
msgstr "重返午夜假面"

msgid "Scenario II: Return to The Midnight Masks"
msgstr "冒险II：重返午夜假面"

msgid "Set the <i>Cult of Umôrdhoth</i> encounter sets aside as a separate “Cultist deck.” Shuffle this deck and remove 3 random cards from it, without looking at them. <i>(You should be left with a 5-card Cultist deck.)</i>"
msgstr "将<i>乌默尔多斯的崇拜者</i>遭遇组放在一边，作为独立的“异教徒牌堆”。混洗异教徒牌堆后，随机移除3张卡牌，不要查看。(<i>剩下的异教徒牌堆应有5张卡牌。</i>)"

msgid "Construct the act deck using one of the two copies of Agenda 1a- \"Predator or Prey\" at random, without looking at their other sides. Remove the other version of Agenda 1a from the game."
msgstr "构建场景与密谋牌堆时，随机选择2个密谋1a - “猎人还是猎物？”其中之一，不要查看另一面。将密谋1a的另一个版本移出游戏。"

msgid "Randomly put 1 of each of the following locations into play: Downtown, Southside, Easttown, Northside, Rivertown, and Miskatonic University. Remove the other versions of those locations from the game. Then, put Graveyeard, St. Mary's Hospital, and Your House into play."
msgstr "从以下地点的多种版本中各随机选择一个放置入场：商业区、南区、东城区、北区、河岸城和米斯卡塔尼克大学。将这些地点的其他所有版本移出游戏。然后，将墓地、圣玛丽医院和你的房子放置入场。"

msgid "Search the gathered encounter sets for any 1-health [[Cultist]] enemy and spawn it at Southside."
msgstr "在找出的遭遇组中，查找任意一个生命值为1的[[异教徒]]敌人，并生成在南区。"

msgid "Search the gathered encounter sets for 2 1-health [[Cultist]] enemies. Spawn 1 at Southside and 1 at Downtown."
msgstr "在找出的遭遇组中，查找2个生命值为1的[[异教徒]]敌人。将其分别生成在南区和商业区。"

msgid "Search the gathered encounter sets for 3 1-health [[Cultist]] enemies. Spawn 1 at Southside, 1 at Downtown, and 1 at the Graveyard."
msgstr "在找出的遭遇组中，查找3个生命值为1的[[异教徒]]敌人。将其分别生成在南区、商业区和墓地。"
